<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Good morning, Richa=
rd,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Thank you for the r=
esponse below. We have referred it to our technical consultant for further =
review and commentary. We will provide that back to you as soon as it is to=
 hand.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Our CEO has been ma=
de aware of this claim externally and will now be briefed on progress as re=
quired.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Regards,<o:p></o:p>=
</span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant.<o:p></o:p></=
