4.5pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><b><i><span lang=3D"FR" style=3D"font-size:1=
1.0pt">Asset Managers</span></i></b><span lang=3D"FR" style=3D"font-size:11=
.0pt"> tender response [Column O =E2=80=93 Tender comparison]<o:p></o:p></s=
pan></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:4.5pt;mso-list=
:l0 level1 lfo1"><b><i><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Arc Projects</span>=
</i></b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"> tender response [Column M =E2=80=
=93 Tender comparison]
<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:=
4.5pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><b><i><span lang=3D"PT-BR" style=3D"font-siz=
