<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hello All,<o:p></o:=
p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Referring to your e=
mail below of December 9.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Are you able to ind=
icate the status of the undertaking of your independent investigations as p=
roposed below.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">We have received 3 =
tender responses back from the reinstatement service providers who attended=
 site with Raffaella and myself late last year.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">As we are all aware=
 we have received these tender responses based on the scope of works provid=
ed by ASURNZ and subsequently shared with all parties.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Agreement on the sc=
ope of works is paramount to claim progression. If we can move to determine=
 the agreed scope for claim related loss =E2=80=93 we can move quickly afte=
rwards to provide the final outcome.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I look forward to a=
n update on your independent enquiries.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Thank you very much=
.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Regards,<o:p></o:p>=
</span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant. &nbsp;&nbsp;=
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
