.0pt">Encapsulate all timber roof structure framing.<o:p></o:p></span></li>=
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:-4.5pt;mso-list:l9 leve=
l1 lfo6"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Remove and replace roofing underl=
ay paper<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"marg=
