t;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">Raffaella
 del Prete &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:raffaellanz@icloud.com">raffaellanz@icloud=
.com</a>&gt;<br>
<b>Sent:</b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>Friday, Octo=
ber 10, 2025 4:53 PM<br>
<b>To:</b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>Grant Metson &=
lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Grant.Metson@tower.co.nz">Grant.Metson@tower.co.nz</a>=
&gt;<br>
<b>Cc:</b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>Abigail Collin=
 &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Abigail.Collin@wynnwilliams.co.nz">Abigail.Collin@wy=
nnwilliams.co.nz</a>&gt;; Richard Hargreaves &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Richard.=
