.nz">Kelly.Mason@tower.co.nz</a>&gt;; Chris Cornwall &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:=
Chris.Cornwall@tower.co.nz">Chris.Cornwall@tower.co.nz</a>&gt;;
 Megan Jensen &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Megan.Jensen@tower.co.nz">Megan.Jensen@=
tower.co.nz</a>&gt;<br>
<b>Subject:</b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>Re: C9030=
6048 - Fire at 23 Mays Street, Devonport [WW-ACTIVE.FID3167762]</span><o:p>=
</o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:1.0pt;color:white">Kia ora =
Grant, Thank you for your email and for confirming receipt of our letter. F=
riday, 17 October after 2:</span><span style=3D"font-size:1.0pt;font-family=
:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:white">=E2=80=8A</span><span style=3D"f=
ont-size:1.0pt;color:white">00
 pm works for me, and I=E2=80=99d appreciate it if testing and assessment c=
ould be scheduled accordingly. I also reserve my right to undertake</span><=
o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:1.0pt;color:white">&nbsp;</=
span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Kia ora Grant,<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Thank you for your email and for confirming receipt =
of our letter.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Friday, 17 October after 2:00 pm works for me, and I=
=E2=80=99d appreciate it if testing and assessment could be scheduled accor=
dingly.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">I also reserve my right to undertake independent tes=
ting and assessment of the property to ensure a full and impartial evaluati=
on.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Having reviewed the proposed plan, I=E2=80=99m conce=
rned the current testing schedule appears incomplete. It does not include t=
he first floor, roof cavity, or the large upper deck, and the basement cove=
rage seems partial, given the known extent
 of smoke, water, and chemical contamination.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">I therefore request confirmation that the planned in=
spection and sampling will be expanded to include all levels and relevant s=
tructural areas. Alternatively, please confirm that Tower will meet my reas=
onable costs should I need to arrange
 independent specialists to carry out supplementary testing (including labo=
ratory analysis).<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Please confirm the final timing for the 17th and the=
 revised scope of testing once available.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Ng=C4=81 mihi,<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Raffaella<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<blockquote style=3D"margin-top:5.0pt;margin-bottom:5.0pt">
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">On 8 Oct 2025, at 5:26<span style=3D"font-family:&qu=
ot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif">=E2=80=AF</span>PM, Grant Metson &lt;<a href=3D"=
mailto:Grant.Metson@tower.co.nz">Grant.Metson@tower.co.nz</a>&gt; wrote:<o:=
p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hello Raffaella and=
 Abigail,</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Thank you for the l=
etter received yesterday at 4:35</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I am replying to ac=
knowledge receipt of the letter, and to further acknowledge that Abigail wi=
ll be copied into all correspondence moving forward.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I have requested th=
at the appointed specialists provide dates and times when they can be avail=
able.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I am proposing that=
 the following persons complete site visit, assessing &amp; testing, as a n=
ecessary pre-requisite to providing relevant reports for all stakeholders t=
o review:</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant Metson</sp=
an></b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0p=
t">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">=E2=80=93 Regional =
Assessing Manager</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Stephen Walker</=
span></b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space"><span style=3D"font-size:11.=
0pt">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">=E2=80=93 Technic=
al Building Consultant. ASURNZ.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Warwick Banks</s=
pan></b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0=
pt">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">=E2=80=93 Associat=
e Structural Engineer. CPEng</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Alexandra Dalzel=
l</span></b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space"><span style=3D"font-size:=
11.0pt">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">=E2=80=93 Fore=
nsic Scientist</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Tyrell Craig</sp=
an></b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0p=
t">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">=E2=80=93 Restorati=
on Cleaning Specialist.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">LBP Builder</spa=
n></b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt=
">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">[ unconfirmed indivi=
dual ] =E2=80=93 we will require the builder to cut inspection
 holes in the wall linings so testing can be completed within the wall cavi=
ties.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The intention is to=
 test for smoke and chemical contamination within the wall cavities, and on=
 the exposed surfaces downstairs. There will be a significant number of sam=
ple sites [tests] to be completed to
 be able to author a reliable report. After initial testing is completed, o=
ur intention is to apply restorative cleaning methods to targeted individua=
l sample sites, followed by subsequent testing, post-cleaning, to provide d=
ata to measure the effectiveness
 of cleaning/decontamination.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">All samples taken f=
rom site will require laboratory analysis before being incorporated into a =
report. This process may take up to 10 working days =E2=80=93 so we want to=
 capture swab samples from surfaces before and
 after the decontamination process is undertaken.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">At this stage we ar=
e looking like being able to conduct this testing onsite, as well as CPEng =
site visit for assessment, on Friday October 17. Time to yet be confirmed.<=
/span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I am unsure from yo=
ur letter attached whether Raffaella and/or other nominated parties wish to=
 be present while this testing and assessment is being conducted. Can you p=
lease confirm for me so that I can complete
 arrangements that will suit all parties who need to be present.</span><o:p=
></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Many Thanks,</span>=
<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant.</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
